  "text": "The salt tolerance of rhizobia was tested on YMA plates containing 2 and 3% (w/v) NaCl. The plates were inoculated with 10 8 cells/ml, and the growth was scored after 12 days at 28°C [CITATION_1] . Tests were done in triplicate.",
